{"tid":1991504,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"金與正嬌喘一聲倒在金正恩嘅懷裏","createTime":"2020-04-27T12:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T14:05:39.000Z","uid":60535,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d264734acc1341e5a18f6f60723f0b210fec512e","tid":1991504,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"金與正嬌喘一聲倒在金正恩嘅懷裏，喺呢個時候，金與正眼如微絲，濕潤嘅雙唇，微微張開，口中噴出有如蘭花一樣嘅香氣......對住如斯尤物，佛都會動心啦。金正恩一手抱腰，另一隻手也不閒住喎，偷偷地從金與正衣襟挖入，係佢豐滿既雙峰附近，周&shy;圍任意遊覽。而金與正既慾火再也控制不住，果兩個釘，亦由軟既棉&shy;花糖變為硬既橡皮糖啦！"},{"pid":"59a83b47b5e509ef90621f894a019e437ea65aec","tid":1991504,"uid":60535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e639adfe06c1e954ae0439ff38a8f364a461703","tid":1991504,"uid":60535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950cf607dbf7eb8e95660adce3728707f38a74a4","tid":1991504,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd4ac945a75e7c1d8148630c838b1ccdc2d13d2","tid":1991504,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033785fd9c6a9f314a5afe9d5d51300ed73f86c5","tid":1991504,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fd4ac945a75e7c1d8148630c838b1ccdc2d13d2","tid":1991504,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b4bed5a0936bb172983e730fc637faf8332371","tid":19915